{"tid":191152,"cid":20,"subCid":0,"title":"[新手]P牌換正式駕照一問","createTime":"2017-04-07T15:32:14.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-13T15:00:50.000Z","uid":104454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"6f14752cb6a6bd11f842a30105c539f5c506e7ff","tid":191152,"uid":104454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-07T15:32:14.000Z","msg":"我上運輸署網站見到寫<br />\n<br />\n<strong>持有暫准駕駛執照（電單車、機動三輛車、私家車或輕型貨車P牌）人士，必須在完成後暫准駕駛期 後的3年內提出申請正式執照，否則，他必須重新報考駕駛考試及完成暫准駕駛期，方可再次申請。</strong><br />\n<br />\n我張P牌寫 16/04/2015 過期<br />\n<br />\n係咪代表我 16/04/2018 前申請都得?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 唔該各位巴打"},{"pid":"d8148942ed97fd15ff387f6645cc8c20d3020996","tid":191152,"uid":33643,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-07T15:36:14.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我上運輸署網站見到寫<br />\n<br />\n<strong>持有暫准駕駛執照（電單車、機動三輛車、私家車或輕型貨車P牌）人士，必須在完成後暫准駕駛期 後的3年內提出申請正式執照，否則，他必須重新報考駕駛考試及完成暫准駕駛期，方可再次申請。</strong><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我張P牌寫 16/04/2015 過期<br />\n<br />\n係咪代表我 16/04/2018 前申請都得?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 唔該各位巴打</blockquote><br />\nyes"},{"pid":"2dedb198f64f69be9769cf79026c3e81e3011735","tid":191152,"uid":24513,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-07T17:40:51.000Z","msg":"快續啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n一陣無左件事 就要考過再掛P"},{"pid":"91190a4710bde576a3c084687dce02d2943c93c9","tid":191152,"uid":99989,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-13T13:35:49.000Z","msg":"得閒就快啲換 唔記得就無了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b6e882243a4c604e269cb8a9a2d17873570b17c8","tid":191152,"uid":44728,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-13T13:38:28.000Z","msg":"樓主竟然浪費咗兩年牌齡<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d2cc1e9bd36a7efe41ad3c8b0c8592e227fe5085","tid":191152,"